	NORFOLK, Neb. (AP) -- Charles P. ``Chuck'' Watson, founder of the  
Vit-E-Men Co., a family operated animal feed and health products 
company, died Monday. He was 69. 
</P>
<P>
	The company, founded in 1970, supplies animal products such as  
hay, silage and inoculates throughout the United States and in 
