<HEADLINE> Streisand To Do New Year's Eve Gig </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LAS VEGAS (AP) -- Barbra Streisand, who christened the MGM Grand  
Garden more than five years ago, is scheduled to return on New 
Year's Eve to usher in the millennium with a rare public 
performance. 
</P>
