longer traded separately, though they remain in use. Based on euro 
rates, the dollar was worth: 1.8344 German marks, down from 1.8394; 
6.1523 French francs, down from 6.1691; 2.0669 Dutch guilders, down 
from 2.0725; 1,816.05 Italian lire, down from 1,821.00. 
</P>
